# ITA - Stato patrimoniale e conto economico\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\n**Italiano**\n\nRendicontazione PDF e XLS per stato patrimoniale e conto economico a sezioni contrapposte.\n\n**English**\n\nPDF and XLS reporting for accounting balance sheets.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nFrom your Accounting / Report section, select \"Account Balance Report\".\n\nThis will trigger a wizard, from which you can setup your report configuration.\nFrom it, you can choose whether should be created, either an HTML interactive view, or a PDF / XLS sheet.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_it_account_balance_report%0Aversion:%2012.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Openforce\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Silvio Gregorini \\<<https://github.com/SilvioGregorini>>\n\n### Other credits\n\nThe development of this module has been financially supported by:\n\n- Odoo Italia Network\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-SilvioGregorini }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-italy](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/tree/12.0/l10n_it_account_balance_report) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_account_balance_report.wizard", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_account_balance_report.wizard.wizard_account_balance_report", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_account_balance_report.wizard..wizard_account_balance_report", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_account_balance_report.wizard.wizard_account_balance_report", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_account_balance_report.wizard.wizard_account_balance_report.REPORT_TYPES", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_account_balance_report.wizard.wizard_account_balance_report.ReportAccountBalanceWizard", "bases": ["models.TransientModel"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_account_balance_report.wizard.wizard_account_balance_report.ReportAccountBalanceWizard.onchange_show_partner_details", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Override to avoid unwanted changes "]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_account_balance_report.wizard.wizard_account_balance_report.ReportAccountBalanceWizard.button_export_html", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_it_account_balance_report.wi